HEADWORD: octahedron
<hw>oc`ta*he"dron</hw> <pr>(⟦ocr⟧k`t⟦adot⟧*h⟦emac⟧"dr⟦ocr⟧n)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>'okta`edron</grk>, fr.
